{"tid":2207263,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰：必需承認，港人擁抱專制。今日的黄色區議員把專制直接實踐，令人嘆息。","createTime":"2020-09-18T04:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T10:29:59.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"776d4941665ea53e58f7ffaa4866b74eda4d68af","tid":2207263,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kO1FwVF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkO1FwVF.jpg&h=47f88032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭松泰：<br />\n《基本法改良芻議》序，題為「必需承認，我們不懂自由。」但經過一連串黄色區議員的拆公園、趕菲傭等事件後，相信大家應該看清現實，該序應改為「必需承認，港人擁抱專制。」<br />\n「專制」不只是描述政權的本質，更廣義的理解是人民的思想文化及道德風尚。在英殖治下，大眾首先學懂的不是「自由」（liberty）及人文精神（humanism），反而是專制的「階級觀念」。<br />\n今日的區議員把專制直接實踐，並應用到日常生活的大小場合之中，令人嘆息。"},{"pid":"00262377fde608df8cf5385cff2912e588ec4bee","tid":2207263,"uid":11097,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:01:34.000Z","msg":"企撚開啦虫太<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4c282bc2668c4bb741c3c50300e59e07cb179c","tid":2207263,"uid":4780,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:02:49.000Z","msg":"係，倒插國旗最反專制"},{"pid":"8579d8ef140106da7c344b394a3521872ec335a8","tid":2207263,"uid":57723,"like":3,"dislike":30,"score":-27,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"絕對無講錯<br />\n個乜春區議員出文反駁國師<br />\n其中一個論點支持自己拆賭檔係因為班廢老係藍絲支持政府<br />\n即係反映2樣野<br />\n1. 個區議員欠缺政治智慧<br />\n2. 黃絲係另一面既極權"},{"pid":"c5b7f1e7984e16583a0c1e969772b19a875c9549","tid":2207263,"uid":56223,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FmBBPKd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFmBBPKd.gif&h=2fc60f65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6bf4a00abb6d74096f4bd86615084022ce3170c","tid":2207263,"uid":7854,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https: